name: Voyager Golden Record
description:
A zip archive is encoded into the image file using least-significant bit steganography.

The zip archive contains the following items sourced from the public domain:
- Various famous photographs widely regarded as being culturally significant
- Audio files containing sounds of Earth such as wind, rain, and various animals
- Text files containing important scientific, philosophical, and literary works

One edition is minted for each of the Voyager missions.
